title: The Sims 8 in 1 on one DvD disk!
description:
This is full pre-activated version of the Sims eight in one on one DvD ISO file.

This is a full verision with no need for a serial or
crack but it may take a long time to install and here
a tip for a quicker installation once you download this
game copy all files on to the hard drive and this take
about 10 min then run setup.exe from the hard drive...

Enjoy, Silichip (UK)
